flowchart TB
    APP[Application]
    DEV[Device Driver<br/>ILI2130]
    BUS[I2C Bus Driver<br/>STM32 I2C Controller]
    MERLIN[Merlin Framework<br/>Platform + Bus + IO Abstractions]
    OS[Camelot-OS API + DTS Metadata]
    HW[Hardware<br/>I2C Controller + I2C Device]

    APP -->|Device-level API| DEV
    DEV -->|i2c_bus_read/write| BUS
    BUS -->|register map GPIO IRQ MMIO| MERLIN
    MERLIN -->|Unified access| OS
    OS --> HW

    MERLIN -. hides non-portable details .-> APP
    MERLIN -. hides non-portable details .-> DEV
